name: SENATUS
overview:
SENATUS is an membership-by-invitation community of influencers - who have the capability of multiplying the effect of ideas, beliefs, knowledge and information through word-of-mouth with their friends, co-workers and the people who intersect their lives.

SENATUS was created with the vision that networking can be done better online and that the platform on which networking is conducted, can be used to enhance the sphere of influence and communication for each and every member.

SENATUS focuses on the aspiring, which simply refers to upwardly mobile professionals and individuals looking to achieve more in their life: from artists, to singers, directors, actors, finance professionals and even writers.

SENATUS was launched in February 2009, with close friends and associates selectively invited for beta testing. Thus far, the network has grown to a membership base of 1,400 members from Singapore, Hong Kong, Shanghai, London, and New York. Comprising finance professionals, designers, entrepreneurs, musicians and directors with one thing in common - an aspiration for success.

milestones.description: SENATUS wins the Gold Award in the Best in Online Media (Magazine) category at the Asian Digital Media Awards, emerging best in entries across Asia-Pacific and Middle East.
milestones.source_description: SENATUS Wins Best Online Magazine at Digital Media Awards
